  "subject": "[SDC] Reduce sdc-be log noise",
  "commit_message": "[SDC] Reduce sdc-be log noise\n\n- set log level for `org.onap.portalsdk.core.onboarding.listener.PortalTimeoutHandler` to `WARN`\n- disable the sdc-be DmaapProducer since dmaap is not part of the ONAP deployment anymore\n- update sdc-workflow-designer image (1.12.0 -> 1.13.2)\n\nIssue-ID: SDC-4731\nChange-Id: Id2d3d2073726ac8c6f3144474f7a76abe24cd5ee\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <Fiete.Ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
